GeneralComments:
$2/hour for charging; free if you are staying in one of their cabins, motel units or tent sites.
24/7
Moeraki Village Holiday Park has several 16 Amp caravan plugs available for daytime charging or charging overnight while you stay in their motel units, cabins or tent sites. You might like to take a 45 minute walk to the famous Mooeraki Boulders while you charge, or visit the local tavern or the well-known Fleurs restaurant,or walk over to the Kaik.
